            "answer_text": "There are 2498 years if you count from December 31 480 BC to December 2018 AD. You shouldn\u2019t subtract 1 from this sum as some people suggest, allegedly because there is no year zero. Indeed there isn\u2019t, but between 1 BC and 1 AD there are 2 years, exactly as there are 2 grade difference between -1 grade and +1 grade Fahrenheit or Celsius scale. ",
